value: Breeds on the Kirghiz Steppes, Transcaspia and parts of Syria, Meso- potamia and Persia. Winters in Egypt, Egyptian Sudan, Sinai and north- western India.

value: Palearctic winter visitor, lake shores and river valleys: Nile Valley south to C Sudan.

breeds damp, vegetated areas near salt or fresh water;also small vegetated islets swampy shores of brackish lakes;lake shores & river valleys, always near water;wet marshy meadows & salt-shrub terrain
